column2: SELECT s.SpecObjID, s.z, s.fiberMag_r, s.sn_#, L.ew, L.sigma, L.sigmaErr into mydb.MyTable from SpecObj as s     JOIN SpecLine as L ON s.SpecObjID = L.specObjID WHERE    (L.LineID = #) AND (L.LineID = #)    and L.ew/nullif(L.ewErr,#)>#   and s.z IS NOT NULL   and s.sn_# > #   and s.objType = # ORDER BY s.mag_#
